Author: Gwang-Jin Kim [aut, cre] (<https://orcid.org/0000-0002-2753-0883>) 
Description: A R6 Class Regreplacer takes a regex pattern containing named groups. 
    It helps to easily retrieve the matched portion by the group name.
    And even to replace the matched portiion of the string by the group name.
